parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument cluster can cause the driver to be unable to see essential gauges, such as the speedometer, fuel gauge, and warning lights, which can lead to accidents, traffic violations, and safety risks.
symptoms: The instrument cluster lights dim or go out
the speedometer and other essential gauges are not visible
and the dashboard lights flicker or fail to illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Airmatic suspension system can cause the vehicle to drop to an undrivable height, making it difficult or impossible to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: the air suspension indicator is illuminated on the instrument panel
the vehicle drops to an undrivable height
the tires rub against the fenders
the vehicle is difficult to steer
and the braking distance is extensively prolonged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument cluster can cause the loss of vital information, such as speed, fuel level, and oil levels, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: the lighting on the instrument panel blinks or stops illuminating
the speedometer and fuel gauge fail to function
the dashboard displays a "cluster failure" message
and the turn signals may not work.
